author: Play On Tabletop
description:
Want to get your own battlefield terrain like what we played here? Check out Fold Forge https://foldforge.etsy.com?coupon=PLAYON12

The Lion and his sons stand against Four Greater Daemons with swords drawn. Founder of Fold Forge, Crockett, has flown to the studio to play on the terrain he produces and brings a heavy Chaos Daemons list that contains two Great Unclean Ones, Shalaxi Helbane, and Be'Lakor. The Dark Angels led by Tak look to send them all back to the warp!

PLEASE NOTE: This game was shot BEFORE we got the Chaos Daemon index update. This much Chaos could not be abandoned so we decided to release it despite the rules being outdated.
